What is the fee structure?

Annual fees: B.Tech - Rs. 2.5 lakhs, MBA - Rs. 4 lakhs, MCA - Rs. 3 lakhs, B.Sc - Rs. 1.5 lakhs. Hostel fees are separate: Rs. 50,000-75,000 per year. We offer scholarships for merit, need-based financial aid, SC/ST waivers (100%), and sports scholarships. Fees can be paid in installments - contact finance office for details.

How can I apply for admission?

Applying for admission to Collegewala is quite straightforward! You can either apply online or in person. To apply online, just visit our website at www.collegewala.edu, fill out the online application form with your details, upload your required documents like mark sheets and ID proof, pay the application fee, and then submit your form. You will receive the merit list within two weeks, and if you're selected, you can complete your admission at our office. If you prefer to apply in person, you can visit our college office during office hours, which are Monday to Friday, from 9 AM to 5 PM.
Thank you for using Collegewala! Your feedback is valuable to us. How would you rate your experience?
What are the eligibility criteria for admission to Collegewala?

B.Tech: 12th pass with PCM (50% aggregate) + JEE Main score. MBA: Any bachelor's degree with 50% marks + CAT/MAT score. MCA: B.Sc/B.Tech with 50% marks. B.Sc: 12th pass with Science stream. Special relaxations available for SC/ST and differently-abled students. If you have concerns about meeting requirements, contact admissions office - they may consider your profile.
